
DAY(1)                                                     DAY(1)

NAME
       day() - returns the name of the day in MUD time

SYNOPSIS
       string day(int x)

DESCRIPTION
       Given a time integer as an argument, this will return the
       day at that time.

EXAMPLES
       day(time()) returns "Shadowday" today

LOCATION
       /secure/sefun/time.c

SEE ALSO
       day(), hour(), minutes(), month(), query_night(), year()

Author
       Descartes of Borg

